<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.7.8">
<l>cīmāli kaṉava ṉōṭu tōḻamai koḷḷavum vallāy</l>
<l>cāmā ṟavaṉainī yeṇṇic cakkarat tāltalai koṇṭā</l>
<l>yāmā ṟaṟiyum pirāṉē yaṇiyaraṅ kattē kiṭantā</l>
<l>yēmāṟ ṟameṉṉait tavirttā yiruvāṭcip pūccūṭṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though you were able to make friends with Śrī Mālika,</l>
<l>Having considered the [best] way for him to die,</l>
<l rend="indent">you took his head with [your] discus.</l>
<l>Lord who knows the future, you dispelled my confusion!</l>
<l>You who sleeps in beautiful Araṅkam,</l>
<l>come so that [I can] adorn [you] with jasmine blossoms!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
